---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import styles from './Experience.module.css'
import tenXLogo from '../assets/images/tenx.webp'
import logiscoolLogo from '../assets/images/logiscool.webp'
import nyxaHostingLogo from '../assets/images/nyxa-hosting.webp'
---

<section class={`fade-in-up ${styles.experience}`} aria-labelledby="experience-heading">
    <h2 class={styles.experience__heading} id="experience-heading">Experience</h2>
    <ul class={styles.experience__list}>
        <li class={styles.experience__item}>
            <Image class={styles.experience__logo} src={tenXLogo} alt="TenX Logo" title="TenX Logo" width="1080" height="1080" loading="eager" decoding="async" fetchpriority="low" />
            <div class={styles.experience__details}>
                <header class={styles.experience__jobHeader}>
                    <h3 class={styles.experience__jobTitle}>TenX · IT Developer</h3>
                    <p class={styles.experience__meta}>July 2025</p>
                </header>
                <p class={styles.experience__description}>I finally had the opportunity to put my skills to the test when I got asked If I could create an application that uses AI to create custom reports for their client based on the type of meeting they had with that client. For one month I dove right in the world of API's, ChatGPT, Python. Each time your application becomes a bit better and more completed. In the end I was super satisfied with the result I worked really hard for.</p>
                <ul class={styles.experience__achievements}>
                    <li>Used a lot of populair frameworks and applications: Next.js, FastAPI, Better Auth, SQLite, Docker.</li>
                    <li>Created a tool that saves an hour on average when it comes to creating a custom made document for the client.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li class={styles.experience__item}>
            <Image class={styles.experience__logo} src={logiscoolLogo} alt="Logiscool Logo" title="Logiscool Logo" width="1080" height="1080" loading="lazy" decoding="async" fetchpriority="low" />
            <div class={styles.experience__details}>
                <header class={styles.experience__jobHeader}>
                    <h3 class={styles.experience__jobTitle}>Logiscool · Teacher</h3>
                    <p class={styles.experience__meta}>July 2022 - May 2026</p>
                </header>
                <p class={styles.experience__description}>For almost three years, I have worked with children between the ages of 7 and 15 in educational settings. I have taught them how to program, create videos, but most importantly, how to think critically and solve problems. My experience has taught me the importance of being able to explain and teach material at each child's developmental level to ensure meaningful learning takes place.</p>
                <ul class={styles.experience__achievements}>
                    <li>Communication is the key to success</li>
                    <li>Explaining and teaching material at child level</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li class={styles.experience__item}>
            <Image class={styles.experience__logo} src={nyxaHostingLogo} alt="Nyxa Hosting Logo" title="Nyxa Hosting Logo" width="1080" height="1080" loading="lazy" decoding="async" fetchpriority="low" />
            <div class={styles.experience__details}>
                <header class={styles.experience__jobHeader}>
                    <h3 class={styles.experience__jobTitle}>Nyxa Hosting · Founder &amp; CEO</h3>
                    <p class={styles.experience__meta}>February 2023 - December 2025</p>
                </header>
                <p class={styles.experience__description}>In the summer of 2020, I decided to start my own hosting company along with a good friend of mine. Within a short time, we had more than 70 clients in over 15 different countries across 5 continents. After a year, I shifted my focus to creating websites for B2B clients. In total, I earned more than €7,000 in less than 2 years while being a student.</p>
                <ul class={styles.experience__achievements}>
                    <li>Sold hosting packages worldwide (70+ customers, 15+ countries, 5 continents)</li>
                    <li>
                        <span>Achieved Top 3 for <a href="https://www.trustpilot.com/categories/web_designer?country=BE" target="_blank" aria-label="Best Web Designer on Trustpilot Belgium">Best Web Designer</a> and <a href="https://www.trustpilot.com/categories/web_hosting_service?country=BE" target="_blank" aria-label="Best Web Hosting Company on Trustpilot Belgium">Best Web Hosting Company</a> (source: Trustpilot)</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
</section>
